covidRaceDataSeparate.latinxNote: Our calculations assume Hispanic or Latino ethnicity may include any race.
covidRaceDataSeparate.mutExclNote: Race categories are mutually exclusive and include both Hispanic/Latino and non-Hispanic/Latino ethnicity.
covidRaceDataSeparate.name: Arkansas
covidRaceDataSeparate.otherNote: One or more standard race categories are not reported or otherwise specified by the state. These categories may or may not be included in the "Other race" category in our data.
covidRaceDataSeparate.popTableNote: Population sizes are taken from the Census Bureaus 2019 ACS 5-Year estimates Table B02001 for race and B03002 for ethnicity.
